prep_novasar[source]

prep_novasar(sedas_supplierId, inter_dir='/tmp/data/intermediate/', s3_bucket='public-eo-data', s3_dir='novasar_uk_test/')

Prepare a Sedas-hosted NovaSAR .zip scene(/strip) by suppliedId into a flavour of ARD using SNAP and upload output COGs to Catapult object storage.
